hey=E2=80=99re=C2=A0Tesla=E2=80=99s preferred way to sell stock, because Te=
sla has enthusiastic retail investors. When Hertz Global Holdings Inc. did =
a stock offering=C2=A0while it was in bankruptcy, to capitalize on baffling=
 (but=C2=A0in hindsight correct!) retail demand, of course=C2=A0it did an A=
TM. The big 2021 meme stocks =E2=80=94=C2=A0GameStop, AMC Entertainment =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0have of course done ATMs.If I ran a micro-cap company and I was=
