ing, but I bet he=E2=80=99s up for it =E2=80=94 that=E2=80=99s like $1.6 bi=
llion of annual revenue for AMC. That=E2=80=99s more than it made selling m=
ovie tickets last year.Or as Aron put it in the press release:To state the =
obvious, one would not normally think that a movie theatre company=E2=80=99=
s core competency includes gold or silver mining. In recent years, however,=
