<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">A gold mine</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We haven=E2=80=99t checked in with AMC=
 Entertainment Holdings Inc. recently; let=E2=80=99s see <a href=3D"https:/=
/link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27034348.257604/aHR0cHM6Ly9pbnZlc3Rv=
ci5hbWN0aGVhdHJlcy5jb20vbmV3c3Jvb20vbmV3cy1kZXRhaWxzLzIwMjIvQU1DLUVudGVydGF=
pbm1lbnQtSG9sZGluZ3MtSW5jLi1Bbm5vdW5jZXMtU2lnbmlmaWNhbnQtSW52ZXN0bWVudC1CdX=
lpbmctMjItb2YtSHljcm9mdC1NaW5pbmctSG9sZGluZy1Db3Jwb3JhdGlvbi9kZWZhdWx0LmFzc=
Hg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb5e5d3ad" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"i=
temscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">what they=E2=80=99re up to</a=
>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">LEAWOOD, Kan.--(BUSINESS WIR=
E)-- AMC Theatres (NYSE:AMC), the largest theatrical exhibitor in the Unite=
d States, in Europe &amp; the Middle East, and in the world, today announce=
d it is buying 22% of Hycroft Mining Holding Corporation (NASDAQ:HYMC) and =
its 71,000 acre Hycroft Mine in northern Nevada. Independent third-party st=
udies confirm that the Hycroft Mine has some 15 million ounces of gold depo=
sits and some 600 million ounces of silver deposit. In addition, AMC will r=
eceive an additional 23.4 million warrants in Hycroft at $1.07 per share. =
=E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Commenting on the investment in H=
ycroft, Adam Aron, chairman and CEO of AMC Entertainment said, =E2=80=9CThe=
 strength of SPIDER-MAN: NO WAY HOME and THE BATMAN, as well as 2022=E2=80=
=99s promising industry box office, heighten AMC Entertainment=E2=80=99s co=
nviction that we are on a glide path to recovery. Our strategic investment =
being announced today is the result of our having identified a company in a=
n unrelated industry that appears to be just like AMC of a year ago. It, to=
o, has rock-solid assets, but for a variety of reasons, it has been facing =
a severe and immediate liquidity issue. Its share price has been knocked lo=
w as a result. We are confident that our involvement can greatly help it to=
 surmount its challenges =E2=80=94 to its benefit, and to ours.=E2=80=9D=C2=
=A0</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ah. Well. I confess that w=
hen I read the headline I assumed it was a Bitcoin mining company? Really i=
t should be a nickel mining company? Strike while the meme iron (nickel) is=
 hot?=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a reason that we have =
not checked in with AMC recently. AMC =E2=80=94=C2=A0and GameStop and Dogec=
oin and non-fungible tokens and the general boom in meme investing=C2=A0=E2=
=80=94=C2=A0was the great financial market story of 2021, but 2022 has<em>=
=C2=A0</em>marked a grim return to normal. These days the market cares abou=
t war and inflation and sovereign default, not whether Adam Aron <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27034348.257604/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cucmVhZG1hcmdpbnMuY29tL3AvYXBlLWFybWllcy1hbmQtaW52ZXN0b3ItcmVsYXRpb25zP3M=
9cg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB8f35fc76" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"=
itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none=
 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">wore pants on a Zoom intervi=
ew</a>. The whole meme-stock thing might have been a function of plentiful =
money and Covid lockdowns, and now it might have run its course. Still =E2=
=80=9CAMC buys a stake in a micro-cap gold miner=E2=80=9D is an incredible,=
 like, final exam for the meme stock era. What on earth!</p><p style=3D"mar=
gin: 16px 0;">First of all, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
com/click/27034348.257604/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9DRU9BZGFtL3N0YXR1cy8xN=
TAzNjkxNzEzNDc0NDAwMjU3/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB7e11bc3d" itemprop=3D"Stor=
yLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; t=
ext-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-co=
lor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">here is =
Aron on Twitter</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">AMC is pla=
ying on offense again with a bold diversification move. We just purchased 2=
2% of Hycroft Mining (NASDAQ: HYMC) of northern Nevada. It has 15 million o=
unces of gold resources! And 600 million ounces of silver resources! Our ex=
pertise to help them bolster their liquidity.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"m=
argin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDiversification=E2=80=9D is something of a dirty w=
ord in modern corporate finance. <em>Investors=C2=A0</em>can diversify. If =
you want to own=C2=A0<em>both=C2=A0</em>a meme-stock movie-theater chain=C2=
=A0<em>and=C2=A0</em>a penny-stock gold mine, you can. You can buy AMC on t=
he stock exchange, you can buy Hycroft on the stock exchange, you can buy b=
oth in any combination you want. Except that now if you buy AMC you also ge=
t some Hycroft, whether you like it or not.[1] Aron buying a chunk of Hycro=
ft for AMC shareholders=C2=A0<em>reduces=C2=A0</em>their choice set.</p><p =
style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One reason for a company to diversify is somethin=
g like: =E2=80=9CWe are in a declining industry, we make good money now but=
 in the long run we worry, so we=E2=80=99d better get into some new industr=
ies with a brighter future.=E2=80=9D A thesis like that for AMC might=C2=A0=
suggest buying a stake in, you know, a streaming service, or a chain of mov=
ie theaters in the metaverse. Use some of AMC=E2=80=99s entertainment-indus=
try expertise to move into an adjacent but more futuristic bit of entertain=
ment. But, nope, a gold mine.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still you can=
 sort of gesture at a diversification rationale here. AMC stock is in some =
sense an ownership share in=C2=A0a chain of movie theaters, but in another =
sense it is a financial instrument that reflects Adam Aron=E2=80=99s abilit=
y to do funny stuff that attracts attention and delights people online. The=
 stock goes up because people online get excited, not because AMC sells mor=
e movie tickets, and so it makes sense for AMC to expand into new and unrel=
ated ways to do funny stuff online.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So buyi=
ng a stake of a gold mine gives AMC some meme diversification. For one thin=
g, this purchase is itself a funny thing that attracts attention and deligh=
ts people online. (AMC=E2=80=99s stock was up about 2.5% as of 11 a.m. toda=
y.) But also, you know, gold has been a meme for millennia; owning a gold m=
ine just gives you many more opportunities to say stuff and attract attenti=
on. =E2=80=9CThe Fed has printed too much money and hyperinflation is aroun=
d the corner, buy movie tickets!=E2=80=9D: sounds weird, right?=C2=A0But =
=E2=80=9C=E2=80=A6=C2=A0buy gold!=E2=80=9D totally works. Just a huge expan=
sion of the meme arsenal.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Next: How many ou=
nces of gold and silver did Hycroft Mining mine and sell last month? If you=
 answered anything other than =E2=80=9Czero,=E2=80=9D you do not understand=
 how meme stocks work. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
lick/27034348.257604/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2=
FyL2RhdGEvMTcxODQwNS8wMDAxMTA0NjU5MjIwMzM1NTYvdG0yMjkxNzZkMl84ay5odG0/607f0=
7ceef4b8524a319a23cB62053fc0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope=
" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">The answer is zero</a>:</p><blockquot=
e><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We are not currently conducting commercial m=
ining operations at the Hycroft Mine. There is no certainty that the minera=
l resources estimated at the Hycroft Mine will be mined or, if mined, proce=
ssed profitably. We have no specific plans and cannot currently predict whe=
n we will be able to bring the Hycroft Mine back into production. The comme=
rcial viability of the Hycroft Mine is dependent on a number of factors, in=
cluding metal prices, the availability of and ability to raise capital for =
development, government policy and regulation and environmental protection,=
 which are beyond our control. We may not generate commercial-scale revenue=
s until we bring the Hycroft Mine back into production.</p></blockquote><p =
style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To be fair, Hycroft <a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/27034348.257604/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9=
kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvMTcxODQwNS8wMDAxNzE4NDA1MjEwMDAxMTAvaHltYy=
0yMDIxMDkzMC5odG0jaTExODI4YjcyNjQ5NTQ4ZDU4YTg2MzMxMmYyYWViZjI0XzE2/607f07ce=
ef4b8524a319a23cBb522244b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" t=
arget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;">sold $31.7 million</a> of gold and silve=
r in the third quarter of 2021; it=C2=A0<em>does=C2=A0</em>own a mine and=
=C2=A0<em>was=C2=A0</em>operating it. But it stopped.[2] A rough <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27034348.257604/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzE3MTg0MDUvMDAwMTEwNDY1OTIwMDU4MDg=
4L3RtMjA3Mjc5LTE0XzQyNGIzLmh0bSN0T1ZF/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB1997ceee" it=
emprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"col=
or: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bo=
rder-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #=
ccc;">corporate history of Hycroft</a> is that it operated a gold mine in N=
evada for a while and then went bankrupt in 2015 due to declining gold pric=
es. While it was bankrupt it stopped mining gold, but it came out of bankru=
ptcy and then started mining=C2=A0again in 2019. And then it stopped again =
late last year.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">During the brief window whe=
n Hycroft was mining gold again, it went public in 2020. Because this is th=
e final exam of meme stocks, you will not be surprised to learn that it wen=
t public by merging with a special purpose acquisition company. It had a li=
mited recent history of producing gold at that point=C2=A0but, because it w=
ent public by SPAC merger, it was able to market itself on=C2=A0<em>project=
